    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1917-09-26T12:29:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1917-09-26T12:29:00-05:00" n="308"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d308">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 837.00/1419</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Minister in Cuba</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Gonzales</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Habana</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1917-09-26T12:00:00-05:29">
                            <hi rend="italic">September 26, 1917, noon.</hi>
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Former President Gomez, leading figure in late revolution who for six months has
                    been confined in penitentiary awaiting trial, has been removed to his country
                    place where he will remain under guard. Board of physicians testified to
                    ex-President’s critical state of health. Mrs. Gomez also ill.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Gonzales</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
